Germany’s Train Drivers Union Calls Strike Over Pay Tomorrow

-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 
2011-02-24T17:24:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/germany-s-train-drivers-union-calls-strike-over-pay-tomorrow.html
  Germany ’s GDL train drivers union
said it will ask employees to hold a nationwide strike tomorrow
to call for a minimum wage across the industry.  The strike is scheduled for between 8:30 a.m. and 11:30
a.m. local time, the union said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
